subSubSection.paragraph: Type locality: Off Shionomisaki, Wakayama Prefecture, Japan

The single
T. kabeyai
sample from Taiwan included in this analysis formed a single cluster that included a sample from off Japan (GN 7431 ) (
Figure 2
). This represents the first sequence record for this species from Taiwan . The species is very distinct from, but sister to, the four
Centroscyllium
species (Supplementary Material 1 ).
